{"tid":1683793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲話有二百萬民意? 真係笑大我個口","createTime":"2019-10-30T19:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T03:09:56.000Z","uid":306826,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2034a94ad3986472f8a7dc7bfbb9dde54aa0a6ca","tid":1683793,"uid":306826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T19:32:39.000Z","msg":"說好的<span style=\"color: red;\">二百萬民意</span>呢?<br />\n大家睇下一個抵制CCTVB嘅Facebook page竟然得<span style=\"color: red;\">兩萬人</span>like<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得<span style=\"color: red;\">1%</span>咋<br />\n到底大家知唔知CCTVB荼毒左幾多人? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求下大家得閒去<span style=\"color: red;\">like</span>同埋做<span style=\"color: red;\">抵制CCTVB嘅任務</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地個個send email嘅決戰任務得幾百封email 難怪CCTVB仲可以存在係香港啦 人地笑緊你地班黃絲冇鬼用呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=eb9986bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb</a><br />\n<br />\nCCTVB就算唔係主線任務 都絕對係個好重要嘅支線任務<br />\n希望大家可以叫埋親朋戚友去like個page同做任務<br />\n期望有一日可以見到<span style=\"color: red;\">CCTVB倒台</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b73erZh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb73erZh.jpg&h=16fdefe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06beb3422e6935f7ce98ebc2541d8036b4b4d53b","tid":1683793,"uid":21920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T19:36:00.000Z","msg":"標題改得好衰但係有用資料"},{"pid":"d6982e725811058efc2a04977fec155bf589660f","tid":1683793,"uid":73137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTi